description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if the 'Vultures 1' album by Ye/Kanye West returns to Apple Music by March 31, 2024 ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

For this market to resolve to "Yes" the 'Vultures 1' album must be made available on Apple Music under its own title. The return of individual tracks as singles or part of different albums or EPs, etc., will not be sufficient to trigger a "Yes" resolution.

If this album is returned to Apple Music but specific songs remain unavailable from it on that platform, this market will resolve to "Yes" provided more than half of the songs are available.

The primary resolution source for this market will be Apple Music, however a consensus of credible reporting will also be used.
